reviewText: Disappointing.  Cheerleaders are the ultimate dream most men.  Fit young and flexible girls.  When most of them talk they tend to be very ditsy and dumb.  And these girls are not wild, they are drunk.  They spend the majority of time arguing with the camera guy about taking off there cloths and when they finally do it is over.  There is a big difference.  I will not be buying another Gone Wild, just not worth the $10!
Contrary to the marketing, this is censored to a degree.  Poor editing and narration.  The girls are hot but not very sexy.  Save your money.
